Ecology.Relationships:
Crows were among the [[favored animal]]s of the [[deities]] [[Gwaeron Windstrom]], [[Mask]], [[Nephthys]], [[Shar]], and [[Brandobaris]].{{Cite web enhancement/Deity Do's and Don'ts|10-14}}

Crows typically harbored animosity towards [[owl]]s.

Crows were commonly considered in cultures to be a bad omen, as well as harbingers of death and misfortune.
